	<term>contextual menu</term>
	<definition><p>A popup <keyword tag="menu">menu</keyword> whose <glossary tag="menu item">menu items</glossary> apply to the object or area that the user clicked.</p>
<p></p>
<p>Contextual menus usually appear when you Control-click (on <glossary tag="Mac OS">Mac OS</glossary> and <glossary tag="OS X">OS X systems</glossary>) or right-click (on <glossary tag="Unix">Unix</glossary> and <glossary tag="Windows">Windows systems</glossary>).</p></definition>
